attributes.Long form description: The student starts to loosen up all the hex socket heads from the bedside table legs. After that, he unscrews all the hex socket head screws from the upper table, and then he detaches the table. Next, the student unscrews all the hex socket head screws from the middle tray, detaches every leg one by one.

attributes.Action sentence: The student loosens some screws of the furniture with an Allen wrench.
The student disassembles the top table.

attributes.Incorrect Action Explanation: Student drops the hex nut accidentally.

attributes.Action sentence: The student disassembles the first leg.

attributes.Incorrect Action Explanation: The student drops the Allen wrench while screwing.

attributes.Action sentence: The student disassembles the second leg.
The student disassembles the third leg.
The student disassembles the fourth leg.
